PURPOSE:-
--------
To Test the operation of route-reflector.


SCENARIO:
----------
Three AS are Present in Scenario.
Node 4, 5, 9, 13, 17 and 21 are configured as BGP SPEAKERS.
BGP SPEAKER 5 is configured as ROUTE-REFLECTOR-CLIENT for BGP SPEAKER 13.


